name: Independent Artist Movement (IAM) Magazine
description: IAM is a magazine that will give you the in-depth scoop on all the fresh, new projects and/or developments in the independent world; through bold, informative, entertaining editorials, behind the scenes footage of not only our own upcoming products, but also books and publications by other independent creators as well. That’s right! This magazine is primarily for you, the independent creator and reader, and the best part is, it’s not just limited to comics! (At least that is the plan.) Its geared at entrepreneurs in all the fields of entertainment from musicians, actors/actresses and models to poets and graphic designers – in short, pretty much any independent venture we are made aware of will be within the pages of IAM Magazine!

name: Bad Ass Tee
description: Fellas let the world know you are a force to be reckoned with! Whether you work in a suit and tie all day or bounty hunt, this tee says it all! You ARE a badass!!!

name: Hot Tale Tee
description: Inspired by our graphic novel about kick butt heroines entitled Hot Tales/Bad Asses, ladies get that firm form fitting hour glass look in this sleek black finely cut sexy tee! Available in sizes Small through XLarge!

name: Russ5377: Project:Prototype
description: The story of Russ5377 is reborn as Jorge Medina brings you Russ5377 Project:Prototype. The story of an orphan who has his memory erased by demented scientists bent on creating the perfect specimen is retold in this 22 page mini comic from MAS Media Studios. Fans of Russ may remember him when the book was released in 2003. Six years later Russ makes a comeback and what a comeback it is!!! Choose from 4 Alternative covers. Cover D
